laboratory_examinations.findings: Initial interalveolar distance was 0.5 cm, improved to 35 mm post-surgery, and maintained at 45 mm at 2 weeks and 6-month follow-up.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Interalveolar distance improved from 0.5 cm to 35 mm immediately post-surgery, and maintained at 45 mm at 2 weeks and 6 months.
